==German==

===Noun===
'''Eibohphobie'''
# [[aibohphobia]], that is, the fear of palindromes

===Usage notes===
The word '''Eibohphobie''' is itself a [[palindrome]].  When actually dealing with individuals that fear palindromes, it is, therefore, advisable to use a different word, such as [[Palindromphobie]].

